{
  "stem": "1733.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 28.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was about three weeks before the end of the war, before we were liberated, which was April.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They load us-- loaded us on a train, about, I think it was 1,200 or 1,400.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody got a full loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were very happy about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we could devour the bread immediately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I know-- I know for a fact, that three weeks later, when we were liberated, we had no food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they didn't feed us at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If the train stopped someplace, at-- at a clearing, they let us off the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They surrounded with SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The people got off the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the-- the grass and the leaves from the trees disappeared immediately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because we ate up the grass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We ate up the leaves, whichever, whatever was edible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At that point, at that point, starvation was very, very great, because we had absolutely no food for three weeks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't give us any-- any food in the transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Germans, the German SS were delighted in torturing us by having cooked potatoes and peeling the potatoes and dropping them on the ground.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And anybody that could jump on that peeling to devour, to eat it up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "People were like animals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People would-- people were eating-- cutting off-- I saw somebody cut-- cut off an ear or break off an ear from somebody and chewing on-- on that flesh.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- at that time-- at that time, I-- I said to myself, if I ever get liberated-- because I had-- the only one that really survived are people that had hope-- if I will ever get enough potato peels in my life, that's all I really would want and want nothing else out of life.",
      "word_count": 59
    }
  ],
